oai_dc:dc.dc:description:
CellDesigner files describing pathogenesis pathways and Cytoscape files describing protein-protein interactions of potential relevance in age-related macular degeneration.

By Fran Pool, Christina Kiel, Luis Serrano and Phil Luthert.

Files can be edited and extended using CellDesigner (http://celldesigner.org) or Cytoscape (https://cytoscape.org) respectively.
